text: haey chaur puok neang roksaa khluon nowknong phteah robsa puok neang haey puok neang kom bangheanh pheap chaetchay dauch pheap chaetchay nei samykal lngongkhlaw dambaung( moun samy ai sla m) aoy saoh . haey chaur puok neang brate b tde sa lat ning brichcheak hsaa kat ning brate b tde tam a l laoh ning anakneasar robsa trong . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh chng bambat pheap kakhvak( babakamm) chenhpi puok anak ao kruosaear na pi. haey trong nung saamat puok anak aoy saatasam
